# Phase 3 Walkthrough: Asset Planning & Creation System

I have completely implemented the **Asset Planning & Asset Creation System** as requested! This new pillar of your Financial OS allows you to proactively plan, score, and track your wealth-generating assets.

> [!TIP]
> The backend automatically restarts and applies schema changes. The new tables (`assets` and `asset_ideas`) have been created. 

## What Was Completed

### 1. The Asset Opportunity Vault
Added a dedicated vault to brainstorm and store potential assets.
- **Asset Scoring System:** A backend algorithm automatically grades each idea from 0 to 100 based on ROI potential, expected time commitment, priority, and risk level.
- **Visuals:** Ideas are displayed as beautiful glass cards with color-coded score badges.

### 2. The Asset Creation Tracker
A pipeline to manage the lifecycle of an asset from planning to active income generation.
- **Roadmap Integration:** Each asset has a direct link to the **Goals & Projects** Kanban board.
- **Financial Tracking:** Quickly see Expected Value vs Actual Monthly Income. 

### 3. The Asset Dashboard
A command center specific to your Asset Portfolio.
- Total Active Assets Value vs Future Portfolio Value.
- Passive Income tracking (Target vs Actual).
- Pipeline Health tracking.

### 4. Kanban Enhancements
- As requested, I built a custom **ResizableSplitPane** component and integrated it into your Goals & Projects Kanban Board. You can now dynamically drag the space between columns!

## Next Steps
You can try navigating to the new **Asset Planning** section in your left sidebar. Try adding an idea to the Opportunity Vault to see its Asset Score calculated automatically!
